<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Velmira - Product Promotion</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #222222;
        }
        
        a {
            color: #3e5c2a;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .email-header {
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #3e5c2a;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .email-body {
            padding: 14px;
            background-color: #f4f3f3;
            min-height: 70vh;
        }
        
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 14px;
            color: #225f1a;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        img {
            padding: 24px;
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
        
        .product-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        
        .product-item {
            background-color: #395f4b;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 15px;
            width: 45%;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .product-item img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .product-img-fallback {
            width: 100%;
            height: 120px;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            display: none;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .product-item h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .product-item p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }
        
        .product-item a {
            background-color: #3e5c2a;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <img src="cid:logo" height="200px" width="200px" alt="Velmira Logo" />
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>
                We are thrilled to introduce some of our featured beauty products just for you. These products are carefully selected to enhance your beauty routine and provide you with the best results.
            </p>

            <div class="product-list">
                <% products.forEach(function(product) { %>
                    <div class="product-item">
                        <img src="<%= product.img %>" alt="<%= product.name %>" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';" />
                        <div class="product-img-fallback" style="display: none;">
                            <span style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; text-align: center;">Image<br>Not Available</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3>
                            <%= product.name %>
                        </h3>
                        <p>
                            <%= product.description %>
                        </p>
                        <a href="<%= product.link %>">Shop Now</a>
                    </div>
                    <% }) %>
            </div>

            <p>
                Stay tuned for more exclusive offers and skincare tips. Thank you for being a radiant part of the Velmira journey!
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>&copy;2025 Velmira. Reflect Your Radiance.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>